    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint, showroom condition. It has been meticulously maintained and looks as if it just rolled off the assembly line. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep shine, and the interior is pristine, showing absolutely no wear or tear. Mechanically, it is perfect; the engine runs smoothly, the transmission shifts seamlessly, and every feature functions exactly as intended. This is a rare find for a buyer seeking a car that has been kept in peak condition since day one.",
